__STREAMING__
@cindex download
@cindex file hosting
@item @b{File hosting:}
__DOWNLOAD__
@cindex streaming
@cindex live
@item @b{Live stream:}
__LIVESTREAM__
@cindex generated
@cindex captcha
@item @b{Link generati dal web (anche dopo captcha):}
__GENERATED__ ed altri servizi
